[@Three_Pounds](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/116058-three_pounds/) actually it's super simple. Your addition is just a simple MM patch:  

    @KERBALRENAMER

    {

      Culture

      {

        // insert name = (new culture) and all the other culture stuff here

      }

    }

You don't have to do anything to KR itself.

